SYSTEM START: 05/19

READING RULES WATER AND ELECTRICITY:

			*Reading should be 1 week before
			*Reading for the present month will be recorded for the past month
				example:
					READING FOR MAY WILL BE RECORDED FOR APRIL

LEGEND:

 [WR] = WATER RATE
 [WU] = WATER UP
 [WD] = WATER DOWN
 [EB] = ELECTRICITY
 [WB] = ELECTRICITY
 [TB] = TOTAL BALANCE
 [LB] = LATEST BALANCE
 [HB] = HAS BALANCE
 [ER] = ELECTRICITY RATE
 [W&E] = WATER AND ELECTRICITY
 [TR] = MONEY TRANSFERRED
 [NTR] = MONEY NOT TRANSFERRED
 [FR] = FOR READING
 [DR] = DONE READING
 [CP] = CASH PAID
 [UFB] = USE FOR BILLS
 [OD] = OVERDUE
 [*] = DOUBLE CHECK / ERROR
 [MWU] = MONEY WITH UNCLE
 [DLY]  = DELAYED
 [MM] = MY MONEY



